Please return ONLY the raw JSON. Do NOT use triple backticks (```), "json" tags, or explanations. Just the JSON output as plain text, no formatting.

The format should be:

[
  {
    "invoice": {
      "invoice_number": "{{INVOICE_NUMBER}}",
      "date": "{{INVOICE_DATE}}"
    },
    "bill_to": {
      "name": "{{BILL_TO_NAME}}",
      "address": "{{BILL_TO_ADDRESS}}",
      "email": "{{BILL_TO_EMAIL}}",
      "phone": "{{BILL_TO_PHONE}}"
    },
    "items": [
      {
        "description": "{{ITEM_DESCRIPTION}}",
        "rate": "{{ITEM_RATE}}",
        "quantity": "{{ITEM_QUANTITY}}",
        "balance": "{{ITEM_BALANCE}}"
      }
    ],
    "total_balance": "{{TOTAL_BALANCE}}"
  }
]
 Key instruction: "Do NOT use triple backticks (`) or format the output as a code block." Follow all the instruction Strictly.

 {{20.json}}
